Example Tutorial i reporduced.
Made from IamTimCorey
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWePkE2ReGw

video is done through WPF. 
i just used Window Forms instead.

Built in Framework 4.5 in Visual Studio 2017

Example Shows connection to two differt apis using  a api static helper class.

Api 1: Returns image based on number passed in. Where no number porvided it gets the latest. 
https://xkcd.com/info.0.json


Api 2: Weather API
Retrieves Sunrise and Sunset times based on lat and long input in connection
https://api.sunrise-sunset.org/json?lat=51.50763954502314&lng=-3.881057118269383


Focus on the project was not the display but about retrieving the Json data. 
